name: Johnny Bravo
description: Johnny Bravo (JBRAVO) is a token inspired by the timeless memories of the '90s, bringing back the essence of childhood for those who grew up watching the adventures of the iconic, egotistical yet lovable character, Johnny Bravo. This token celebrates the carefree days of youth, where Saturday morning cartoons, humor, and larger-than-life personalities like Johnny Bravo reigned supreme.
